init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Our leader is John Krasinski, who calls himself “Big Daddy”.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien was able to escape, but left behind a small chip.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I flew the helicopter to the coordinates, which was an apartment building in New York City.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I turned on the lights, and shouted my order again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens were not so calm.
